{"tid":1565434,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"祝各位手足中秋節快樂","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T07:10:35.000Z","uid":2634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e876e9ccdef84dbdf54c5f8b3eb73d3cf413d5","tid":1565434,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"今日係中秋節，各位手足不彷<strong>今日</strong>輕鬆下，休息下，為之後嘅路唞足精神。休息完之後，就要更加醒目同更加醒神咁打一場美好嘅仗。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家謹記以下幾點<br />\n1. 五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n2. 不分化，不割席，不篤灰。<br />\n3. 必須Fact Check所有消息同資料。<br />\n4. <strong>唔好輕敵</strong>，唔好睇少對家。<br />\n5. <strong>要謙卑</strong>，經常自我反思同檢討，不斷改進。<br />\n6. <strong>唔好俾短暫嘅好消息沖昏頭腦。</strong><br />\n7. <strong>勿忘初衷！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">謙卑，謙卑，再謙卑</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n希望出年嘅中秋，大家都可以無悔今日嘅信念同行動！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>願出年嘅中秋，榮光歸香港！</strong></span></span></div><br />\n大家中秋節快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/69624618_2391977174354082_5817167170072367725_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;oh=f3ca52f8a1490f374c1ad2fa1ef14b75&amp;oe=5E042CFB&amp;ig_cache_key=MjExNzEyOTU2MDQxNTAzMzA2Mg%3D%3D.2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fv%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F69624618_2391977174354082_5817167170072367725_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D106%26oh%3Df3ca52f8a1490f374c1ad2fa1ef14b75%26oe%3D5E042CFB%26ig_cache_key%3D